Jo, Charlie,

    I have an idea for an invention that I am very enthusiastic about.  =
If you get time from your other responsibilities here or there, please =
take a minute two start seeing if this has been done before with some =
searches. =20

   You know those little plastic golf balls filled with liquid that you =
freeze and use as ice cubes?  I want to do jacks.  You know, like jacks =
that little kids play with?  And a ball to go with it.  The thinking is, =
jacks have a lot more surface area than balls - imagine how quickly they =
would cool down a frosty drink !  And, here's the best part, the kids =
could play with them while they were not being used for the primary =
purpose.

I think this shows a lot of promise - let me know if you find anything.

Thanks

Pat
